HEADWORD: extremum
<hw>extremum</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the point located
farthest from the middle of something.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> extreme point, extreme, extremity.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>the most extreme possible amount or value.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> peak.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Extricable</ent>⟦br⟧
